Joe Chrest is an American academic and actor. He has had roles in numerous films and television shows including 21 Jump Street, 22 Jump Street, Oldboy, Lee Daniels' The Butler, The Perfect Date, and as Ted Wheeler in Stranger Things.


== Early life ==
Chrest was born and raised in St. Albans, West Virginia, where he attended St. Albans High School.


== Personal life ==
Chrest is also a professor at LSU School of Theatre.


